<Body>  <Title>合川百年小吃店起大火 疑因厨师炒咸菜导致</Title>
	<ReportTime type="absTime">2009年07月16日</ReportTime>
	<Content>	

		<Paragraph>
                <Sentence>
                <Event type="thoughtevent" eid="e1"><Participant sid="s1">本报</Participant><Denoter type="statement" did="d1">讯</Denoter></Event> 
                （记者 裘晋奕）
                <Event eid="e2">
                <Time type="relTime" tid="t2">昨晨6点过</Time>
                ，
                <Location lid="l2">合川区柏树街78号居民楼下临街抄手店</Location>
                突发
                <Denoter type="emergency" did="d2">大火</Denoter>
      </Event>
  ，<Event eid="e3"><Object sid="s3">浓烟</Object><Denoter type="movement" did="d3">直冲</Denoter><Location type="destination" lid="l3">楼上</Location></Event>，
  <Event eid="e4">
  <Participant sid="s4">57户居民</Participant>
  全部
  <Denoter type="stateChange" did="d4">惊醒</Denoter>
  </Event>
  ，
  <Event eid="e5">
  <Participant sid="s5">不少人</Participant>
  还
  <Denoter type="action" did="d5">吸入</Denoter>
  <Object oid="o5">大量烟雾</Object>
  </Event>，咳嗽一上午都未见好转。</Sentence></Paragraph>

　　<Paragraph>
<Sentence>
<Event eid="e6">
<Time type="relTime" tid="t6">上午11点过</Time>
，
<Participant sid="s6">记者</Participant>
<Denoter type="movement" did="d6">赶到</Denoter>
<Location lid="l6">事发现场</Location>
时
</Event>
，
<Event eid="e7">
<Object oid="o7">大火</Object>
已被
<Denoter type="stateChange" did="d7">扑灭</Denoter>2个多小时</Event>
。
</Sentence>
<Sentence>
不过，
<Event eid="e8">站在<Location lid="l8">距离出事门面10米远处</Location>，就能<Denoter type="perception" did="d8">闻到</Denoter>一股浓烈的<Object oid="o8">焦糊气味</Object></Event>
。
</Sentence>
<Sentence>
<Event type="thoughtevent" eid="e9"><Participant sid="s9">记者</Participant><Denoter type="perception" did="d9">看到</Denoter></Event>
，
<Event eid="e10">出事门面叫做<Object oid="o10">吕氏鸡肉抄手店</Object>，<Time type="relTime" tid="t10">当时</Time>已经<Denoter type="stateChange" did="d10">关门歇业</Denoter></Event>
，
<Event eid="e11"><Location lid="l11">门上</Location><Denoter type="action" did="d11">贴</Denoter>着一纸落款为7月15日的<Object oid="o11">致歉告示</Object></Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph>

　  <Paragraph>
<Sentence>据了解，失火的吕氏鸡肉抄手店系合川名小吃，在当地已有百年历史。</Sentence>
<Sentence>
<Event type="thoughtevent" eid="e12">合阳城街道办事处安监办<Participant sid="s12">王先生</Participant><Denoter type="statement" did="d12">介绍</Denoter></Event>
，
<Event eid="e13">发生<Denoter type="emergency" did="d13">火灾</Denoter></Event>后，
<Event eid="e14"><Participant sid="s14,s15">工作人员</Participant>也<Denoter type="movement" did="d14">赶到</Denoter><Location lid="l14">现场</Location> </Event>
<Event eid="e15"><Denoter type="operation" did="d15">维持</Denoter><Object oid="o15">秩序</Object></Event>
。
</Sentence>
<Sentence>
“<Event eid="e16"><Time type="relTime" tid="t16">出事时</Time>，有<Participant sid="s16">厨师</Participant>在<Denoter  type="operation" did="d16">炒制</Denoter><Object oid="o16">咸菜</Object></Event>，可能就是因此起火的。”
</Sentence></Paragraph>

　　<Paragraph>
<Sentence>
<Event type="thoughtevent" eid="e17">
<Time type="relTime" tid="t17">同时</Time>，合川区市政委市政监察执法大队的<Participant sid="s17">高队长</Participant><Denoter type="statement" did="d17">证实</Denoter></Event>
，
<Event eid="e18"><Object  oid="o18">吕氏抄手店</Object>之前就因违章搭建多次受到<Denoter type="operation" did="d18">处理</Denoter></Event>，不过起火原因是否与违章搭建有关，
<Event eid="e19"><Participant sid="s19">合川消防支队和当地警方</Participant>已介入<Denoter type="operation" did="d19">调查</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph>



